Task 4 - Weekend vs Weekday Sales Analysis

Objective
The objective of this task was to compare weekend and weekday sales performance during Q4 2022 and evaluate the effectiveness of promotional campaigns across different months.

Tools Used
- Python
- Excel
- Looker Studio

Dataset Features Used
- order_date
- before_discount
- month_name
- day_name
- year

Analysis Performed
Sales data from October, November, and December 2022 was analyzed by separating weekday and weekend transactions. Average sales values were calculated and compared month-wise to identify customer purchasing trends and seasonal sales performance.

Visualization
Python visualizations and Looker Studio dashboards were created using bar charts, pie charts, KPI scorecards, and comparison visuals to present Q4 sales trends clearly.

Key Insights
Weekday sales remained stronger during most of Q4 2022, while December showed noticeable improvement in weekend sales performance due to seasonal demand and promotional campaign activity.

